wisediff bundles the following third-party open-source libraries in `src/vendor/`.
They are redistributed UNMODIFIED (bundled ESM builds fetched via jsDelivr `+esm`) and are
inlined verbatim into `dist/index.html` by `scripts/build.mjs`. Both licenses are permissive
and compatible with the MIT License. No GPL/AGPL code is redistributed. npm dependencies are
not used at runtime.

